Annotations.ValidationAttribute.ErrorMessage%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> is provided in the validation attribute."},{"content":"The resource file is stored in the App_LocalResources folder.","pos":[47874,47935]},{"pos":[47941,48143],"content":"The name of the localized resources file has the form <ph id=\"ph1\">`DataAnnotation.Localization.{`</ph><bpt id=\"p1\">*</bpt>name<ept id=\"p1\">*</ept><ph id=\"ph2\">`}.resx`</ph>, where <bpt id=\"p2\">*</bpt>name<ept id=\"p2\">*</ept> is a culture name in the format <bpt id=\"p3\">*</bpt>languageCode<ept id=\"p3\">*</ept><ph id=\"ph3\">`-`</ph><bpt id=\"p4\">*</bpt>country/regionCode<ept id=\"p4\">*</ept> or <bpt id=\"p5\">*</bpt>languageCode<ept id=\"p5\">*</ept>.","source":"The name of the localized resources file has the form `DataAnnotation.Localization.{`*name*`}.resx`, where *name* is a culture name in the format *languageCode*`-`*country/regionCode* or *languageCode*."},{"pos":[48149,48375],"content":"The key name of the resource is the string assigned to the <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ValidationAttribute.ErrorMessage%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType&gt;</ph> attribute,  and its value is the localized error message.","source":"The key name of the resource is the string assigned to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations.ValidationAttribute.ErrorMessage%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> attribute,  and its value is the localized error message."},{"content":"For example, the following data annotation attribute defines the default culture's error message for an invalid rating.","pos":[48377,48496]},{"content":"You can then create a resource file, DataAnnotation.Localization.fr.resx, whose key is the error message string and whose value is the localized error message.","pos":[48870,49029]},{"content":"The file must be found in the <ph id=\"ph1\">`App.LocalResources`</ph> folder.","pos":[49030,49088],"source":" The file must be found in the `App.LocalResources` folder."},{"con