ooling.md)."},{"content":"This behavior is not desirable when connecting to Azure SQL Databases, since connection attempts can fail with transient errors that are typically recovered quickly.","pos":[63823,63988]},{"content":"To better optimize the connection retry experience, the connection pool blocking period behavior is removed when connections to Azure SQL Databases fail.","pos":[63989,64142]},{"content":"The addition of the new <ph id=\"ph1\">`PoolBlockingPeriod`</ph> keyword lets you to select the blocking period best suited for your app.","pos":[64144,64261],"source":"The addition of the new `PoolBlockingPeriod` keyword lets you to select the blocking period best suited for your app."},{"content":"Values include:","pos":[64262,64277]},{"content":"The connection pool blocking period for an application that connects to an Azure SQL Database is disabled, and the connection pool blocking period for an application that connects to any other SQL Server instance is enabled.","pos":[64333,64557]},{"content":"This is the default value.","pos":[64558,64584]},{"content":"If the Server endpoint name ends with any of the following, they are considered Azure SQL Databases:","pos":[64585,64685]},{"content":".database.windows.net","pos":[64689,64710]},{"content":".database.chinacloudapi.cn","pos":[64714,64740]},{"content":".database.usgovcloudapi.net","pos":[64744,64771]},{"content":".database.cloudapi.de","pos":[64775,64796]},{"content":"The connection pool blocking period is always enabled.","pos":[64859,64913]},{"content":"The connection pool blocking period is always disabled.","pos":[64975,65030]},{"pos":[65032,65069],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Enhancements for Always Encrypted<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**Enhancements for Always Encrypted**"},{"content":"SQLClient introduces two enhancements for Always Encrypted:","pos":[65071,65130]},{"content":"To improve performance of parameterized queries against encrypted database columns, encryption metadata for q