es.NamedPipeClientStream.ConnectAsync%2A>."},{"content":"method.","pos":[110175,110182]},{"pos":[110190,110243],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>EventSource now supports writing to the Event log<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**EventSource now supports writing to the Event log**"},{"content":"You now can use the <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource&gt;</ph> class to log administrative or operational messages to the event log, in addition to any existing ETW sessions created on the machine.","pos":[110254,110454],"source":"You now can use the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource> class to log administrative or operational messages to the event log, in addition to any existing ETW sessions created on the machine."},{"content":"In the past, you had to use the Microsoft.Diagnostics.Tracing.EventSource NuGet package for this functionality.","pos":[110455,110566]},{"content":"This functionality is now built-into the .NET Framework 4.6.","pos":[110567,110627]},{"content":"Both the NuGet package and the .NET Framework 4.6 have been updated with the following features:","pos":[110638,110734]},{"pos":[110746,110764],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Dynamic events<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**Dynamic events**"},{"content":"Allows events defined \"on the fly\" without creating event methods.","pos":[110779,110845]},{"pos":[110857,110874],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Rich payloads<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**Rich payloads**"},{"content":"Allows specially attributed classes and arrays as well as primitive types to be passed as a payload","pos":[110889,110988]},{"pos":[111000,111021],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Activity tracking<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**Activity tracking**"},{"content":"Causes Start and Stop events to tag events between them with an ID that represents all currently active activities.","pos":[111036,111151]},{"pos":[111162,111340],"content":"To support these features, the overloaded <ph id=